      "text": "ただいま、お母さん\n……こっちに戻って来るのも、なんだか久しぶりね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m home‚ Mom.\n…It feels like it’s been a while since I came back here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1666670799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_nagaseent-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "nagaseent-00-night",
      "startTime": 30.0421328862
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
