      "text": "連絡くらいマメにしなさいって……分かってるんだけど\n最近、スケジュールが詰まっててあんまり暇がなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know you tell me to stay in touch more often…\nbut my schedule’s been packed lately‚ and I haven’t had much time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2666670799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mna_07_01-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でも明日までは、こっちでゆっくり出来るから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But I can relax here until tomorrow.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9864863396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
